name: The Henogram in Red
description:
The Henogram in Red
"Help me, Obi-Wan Henobi. You're my only hope."

Princess Lay-a's famous message to Obi-Wan Henobi, depicted in this iconic series of 5 NFTs:

The Henogram in Red
The Henogram in Green
The Henogram in Blue
The Henogram in Yellow
The Henogram in Pink

Remember. You don't find the Henogram. The Henogram finds you.
